Scenario: Test DcRsp model
Given a DcRsp model
When DcResp status is set to 0
Then DcResp xml string should be {<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?><DcRsp><Status>0</Status></DcRsp>}

When DcResp status is set to 1
Then DcResp xml string should be {<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?><DcRsp><Status>1</Status></DcRsp>}

Scenario: Test the DC Response by running the Consoloidation
Given an instance of Consolidation Resource
Given a batch of values for System Configuration named CONSOLIDATION_TABLES_EMPTY.xml
When the WebAPI Starts Up

When a {EMPTY} POSLog xml has been consolidated

Given a batch of values for System Configuration named TXL_POSLOG_DCRESP.xml

Then DcResp xml string should be {<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?><DcRsp><Status>2</Status></DcRsp>}

When a {CORRECT} POSLog xml has been consolidated
Then DcResp xml string should be {<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?><DcRsp><Status>0</Status></DcRsp>}

When a {ABNORMAL} POSLog xml has been consolidated
Then DcResp xml string should be {<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?><DcRsp><Status>0</Status></DcRsp>}